tēmu, tāpēc, lai rastu citu risinājumu – ventilācijas sistēmu izvadītu uz Dzemdību nama jumta, pēc Pasūtītāja pieprasījuma Izpildītājs izstrādāt būvprojekta daļu “Būvkonstrukcijas”. Minēto, no pusēm neatkarīgo un objektīvo apstākļu dēļ, ir notikusi kopējā būvprojekta izstrādes aizkavēšanās, jo citas Būvprojekta daļas Projektētājs ir pabeidzis un iesniedzis Pasūtītājām Līgumā paredzētajā termiņā.    ","description":"1.\tPagarināt Līguma kopējo projektēšanas izpildes termiņu līdz 15.11.2024","value":70000,"winnerName":"SIA \"OZOLA & BULA, arhitektu birojs\"","sourceUrl":null,"date":null,"name":"Būvprojekta izstrāde un autoruzraudzība Dzemdību nama operāciju blokam"}]}},"flaggedLots":[{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104249","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EKEIS/Supplier/Procurement/107796"}},{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104269","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EKEIS/Supplier/Procurement/107796"}},{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104289","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EKEIS/Supplier/Procurement/107796"}},{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104292","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EKEIS/Supplier/Procurement/107796"}},{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104293","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EKEIS/Supplier/Procurement/107796"}},{"indicator":"B1","scope":"lot","buyerId":"40003194600","status":"RiskFound","level":"yellow","score":null,"lotId":"104295","detail":{"receivedBids":1,"sourceUrl":"https://www.eis.gov.lv/EK